  "OpenLP Website": "",
  "OpenLP is free, open-source presentation software designed for churches. This plugin allows ChurchCRM to send notifications and alerts directly to your OpenLP display.": "",
  "Person/Family Integration": "",
  "Phone Number Format": "",
  "Phone numbers should be in E.164 format: country code + number. Examples:\n- US: +14155551234\n- UK: +447700900123\n- Australia: +61412345678\n\nRecipient phone numbers in ChurchCRM member profiles should include the country code for SMS to work correctly.": "",
